## Cost Management

**Budget targets** (set per your project)
- Dev: < ${DEV_BUDGET}/month
- Staging: < ${STAGING_BUDGET}/month
- Production: per-agent tracking with alarms on daily spend

**Tactics (see `cost-optimizer` skill for depth)**
- Model routing per task complexity
- Provider-side prompt caching for stable system prompts (~90% input discount on cached portion)
- Application caching for repeated queries (DynamoDB with TTL)
- Tight `max_tokens` per call site (output tokens dominate cost)
- Cost telemetry per agent / task / tenant for ongoing optimization

